title: ТилиТелеТесто с Ларисой Гузеевой
overview: This is a culinary show, after watching which housewives will learn how best to beat cream - with a whisk or fork, what should be added to the dough - sugar or powder, how to properly knead pancakes - clockwise or counterclockwise, in general, they will receive comprehensive answers to all burning questions questions arising in the kitchen.
